
** Information

  - v$sga
  - v$sgainfo
  - v$process
  - v$instance
  - v$session

** Session

  <verbatim>
    SQL> alter session set sql_trace = true;
  </verbatim>

  <verbatim>
    SQL> execute dbms_system.set_sql_trace_in_session(sid, serial#, TRUE);
  </verbatim>

  - The files will be written to the udump directory.
